Significantly, women are far less perturbed by picking the right wine with only six per cent listing it as the thing that makes them most uncomfortable.

In terms of day-to-day events that make us feel uncomfortable, spiders still give us the creeps – almost one in six (16 per cent) of us admit to being scared by them.  

There are things even more unnerving than spiders and wine but, thankfully, they are not likely to crop up quite as much.

